window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>I </b><b><i>almost</i></b><b> hooked up with a werewolf… but before we got to third base, he dragged me off to jail.</b></p> <p>Apparently, he's the leader of the pack in town.</p> <p>The fact that I’m an illegal blood wolf—a vampire/werewolf hybrid—doesn’t help my case.</p> <p>And he didn't appreciate me accidentally biting him when we were kissing, either.</p> <p>Luckily, or unluckily, he seems to think I'm his true mate, which means he won't let anyone hurt me.</p> <p>But he also won't let me go.</p> <p>Between his possessiveness, my need to be near him, and the vampire clan hunting me, one thing's becoming clear:</p> <p>I won't be able to avoid my werewolf forever.</p> <p><b><i>This is a steamy, fun full-length standalone romance with a happily ever after!</i></b></p>"; 
